Her idol is Kim Clijsters and the youngster says she models her game style and energy after the four-time major champion, though an adorable picture shows a tiny Cici posing with Maria Sharpova just three years ago. 

'It's crazy to think that I'm actually here right now with all these other people,' she said of Tuesday's match. 

'I never thought I would be practicing or sharing a court with a player that I watch on TV frequently. It's crazy. But I love it.'

 

